\\\",\\\"match\\\":\\\"popular\\\"}],\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":288}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"f4b0976b-fae6-387b-8f8e-0c1e902476f0\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":48}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"c72d5aa0-ea4b-30da-9f98-4cebbb356ec7\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":47}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"42ada487-b2df-4ab6-ad2e-e265119f8280\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"source\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"list\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"e696d598-9d25-4bec-80f7-d79837708a43\\\"},\\\"is_pinned\\\":true}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"607aaa48-bc48-3f2b-a7a4-076787579953\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=cavideo\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":9,\\\"is_pinned\\\":true}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"f768fa17-def1-3624-8ef8-c21ffb48b74b\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":115}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"98444be4-0afc-3bb1-8116-6347f94a68ef\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":177}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"a7909f46-27f0-36e4-84d5-190a43bf6fec\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":90}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"0a283b1e-ccb1-479e-8ed7-2427a06ac0fd\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"65232796-98ca-466b-abd4-5e8532071fbf\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"51f8c669-41d7-355c-b93e-8b790d79048c\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":1956}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"521f0901-2e1e-36d6-beea-a3bbc2439d21\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":13}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"12210e5c-6e9d-339b-bd3f-14511ee45a9b\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":28}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"e2f45936-7155-3464-a9af-c7454f9a2fc7\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":16}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"3e002a9e-d17f-30c9-8aa9-d6d8796989e8\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":269}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"fbd0631d-b20c-3253-bf26-fe9fac17413e\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":162}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"1bb03e8b-7802-3f9a-8213-c1c2ac478ee2\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":8}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"e72a97bb-ef37-3167-b65a-47b9cd44f632\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":148}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"00b257d3-f9f4-3e53-9c8a-798511623a6f\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=cavideo\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":1,\\\"is_pinned\\\":true}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"c578ad96-402a-440b-8d7a-0568e588a6fe\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"source\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"list\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"e696d598-9d25-4bec-80f7-d79837708a43\\\"},\\\"is_pinned\\\":true}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"0e359814-7a6c-3ab6-81c0-121aaa6484e6\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":34}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"e5b90f6d-519c-33ce-8e47-8980c3d4aade\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":18}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"f464d936-c7e0-3bb0-9d36-5a04d15fdc56\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":40}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"ac82356d-ecb9-3cfd-b844-934b9c3a4222\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":919}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"87dda853-7222-3de1-a21a-49642a8e5d14\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":24}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"fd9e5ff4-c257-3ff4-aa57-7880842dabd5\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":239}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"74cd54ca-7928-3b80-9540-842163898a0f\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":137}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"f7d6b09f-7921-3552-b2ec-2efcf25a4827\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":40}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"739133cd-a5eb-396d-ab7e-4495e3484a63\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":134}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"53f13a8a-2e91-39e9-9fb8-8cccb23d0d75\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":605}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"4a144faa-2cd4-3e19-9931-17192217c55c\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":12}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"859a3e75-ae50-3a0e-acc8-6e1e102d9dd7\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":133}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"e711d06e-74d6-3489-b017-4df8aacb39f8\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":115}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"96f11924-f1b7-3dc6-9f15-7aa93325a176\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":12}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"e0a359c8-69b8-34e4-b584-7315bbdc53bb\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":845}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"1eda223f-a289-4f4b-94fb-d4e5b82777f0\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"source\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"list\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"e696d598-9d25-4bec-80f7-d79837708a43\\\"},\\\"is_pinned\\\":true}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"6c33f872-7cdc-306e-8ae9-afa1be2fcde3\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":3}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"1ceb0e03-38d8-3dc9-abb3-e57acfea1070\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":377}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"7750d5fd-c79a-3fc4-b8a4-79ff43833cbd\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":37}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"a3e7c014-3e01-3f1b-a441-8b4fb6d4ca4b\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":3}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"913a82fc-92ce-3c2e-9414-cb809227e103\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=cavideo\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":9,\\\"is_pinned\\\":true}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"e3b4433f-01dc-378c-b1cd-2781844b5170\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":47}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"537cba84-ce3d-339f-97b2-4d71ffe0edcb\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":69}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"d95a7d28-978a-3173-b64d-ef526ad9bf06\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":105}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"67455ffa-d36b-4d38-b5c1-746e1a4255de\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"1def93f5-d7d7-37d7-8431-ff6a7e59a21d\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":20}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"cf023301-3ac1-3ad8-848a-0c38456f4b5e\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"reasons\\\":[{\\\"id\\\":\\\"cf023301-3ac1-3ad8-848a-0c38456f4b5e\\\",\\\"match\\\":\\\"popular_in_geo\\\"}],\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":783}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"7fd3456a-cea8-30ab-8ce0-dca8ce0a207f\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":35}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"34889423-7882-3b3d-8e51-5fe2a1163d60\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":63}},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"6b412c78-ba5b-36fb-ac06-fb4b2908904b\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=cavideo\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":16,\\\"is_pinned\\\":true}}],\\\"seenHits\\\":[{\\\"id\\\":\\\"e47addcc-3ea2-302a-b61c-e4e5708ebfd2\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"ymedia:type=story\\\",\\\"reasons\\\":[{\\\"id\\\":\\\"e47addcc-3ea2-302a-b61c-e4e5708ebfd2\\\",\\\"match\\\":\\\"popular\\\"}],\\\"metadata\\\":{\\\"comment_count\\\":354,\\\"is_pinned\\\":true}}],\\\"expId\\\":\\\"megastream_unified__en-US__frontpage__default__default__desktop__ga__noSplit\\\",\\\"sessionId\\\":\\\"1t555c1kr2ne2_1773231554385\\\",\\\"lastVespaRequestTimestamp\\\":1773231554304,\\\"shouldGridLog\\\":false}}\"])<\/script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"5f:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-3 sm:px-4 md:px-0\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L61\\\",null,{\\\"enabled\\\":true,\\\"initialPreferences\\\":{\\\"cardSize\\\":\\\"small\\\"},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L62\\\",null,{\\\"aiCommentSummaries\\\":{\\\"summaries\\\":{\\\"8fe97f0c-0803-30ea-b86c-ac6ece676018\\\":\\\"Comments include concerns that President Trump’s policies, including tax cuts for the wealthy and increased military spending, are driving unsustainable national debt growth, with some noting a pattern of Republican-led deficits and others calling for tax reforms and spending cuts to address the crisis. The discussion also includes criticism of the lack of investment in social programs amid rising borrowing.\\\",\\\"5d1c0e20-d6de-3e84-8565-6a3de5c94b21\\\":\\\"Comments include support for the Alabama governor’s decision to commute the death sentence, citing fairness since the actual shooter avoided execution. Other comments point to concerns about the felony murder rule’s fairness and praise the governor’s common-sense approach.\\\",\\\"522dba52-cdbb-42f7-94f0-2e162ad95fb8\\\":\\\"Comments include skepticism about Maxx Crosby’s failed physical and its impact on his trade value, with some suggesting the Ravens used it as an excuse to back out due to salary cap or roster concerns. Other comments point to the Raiders’ struggles with trades and cap space, while some anticipate teams like the Cowboys or 49ers might still pursue Crosby.\\\",\\\"9173b898-a466-3c46-88a6-b4e6f7423851\\\":\\\"Comments include criticism of Mickey Rourke's financial choices and eviction for unpaid rent, with some noting his refusal of a GoFundMe set up without his consent. Other comments point to his past success and question how he manages money now, while a few express sympathy for his situation.\\\",\\\"43646736-cbcf-3083-b71b-7da608879373\\\":\\\"Comments include views that the prank was a tragic accident and the teens didn’t intend harm, with some urging no charges but community service or restitution. Other comments stress accountability, arguing charges are necessary to honor the victim’s family and uphold justice.\\\",\\\"b70af900-6a2a-3b9a-8b85-01dbb742d792\\\":\\\"Comments include criticisms of ethics violations and transactional loyalty within President Trump’s circle, highlighting how Kristi Noem’s ouster and revoked Mar-a-Lago membership reflect his self-serving approach. Other comments point to her misuse of taxpayer funds and the pattern of Trump discarding former allies.\\\",\\\"c537abaa-aafa-383e-b3d1-d2408b8ba491\\\":\\\"Comments include claims that President Donald Trump is upset not over corruption but because Corey Lewandowski profited without giving Trump a cut, with many alleging widespread profiteering and nepotism in the administration. Other comments point to calls for independent investigations and comparisons to past corruption.\\\",\\\"b1c23951-272a-3252-8e15-5e6f0e353ba0\\\":\\\"Comments include widespread skepticism about Erika Kirk’s qualifications, with many asserting her appointment reflects President Trump’s pattern of favoring loyalty and appearance over expertise. Other comments point to concerns about cronyism, lack of experience, and political motives behind such government appointments.\\\",\\\"926e0476-96b3-373a-8364-6bcd35ec73ce\\\":\\\"Comments include many questioning how a dine-and-dash could happen at Golden Corral since payment is required upfront, with some doubting the $15,000 claim for brain injury and others suggesting the amount is too low. The discussion also includes skepticism about the story's details and calls for more accountability.\\\",\\\"93805f39-7fab-4cf8-b207-a249c867a3f8\\\":\\\"Comments include skepticism about the accuracy and value of the mock draft, with many questioning player rankings and team needs, especially regarding quarterbacks and offensive line picks. Other comments point to Ohio State’s strong presence in the draft and debate over the Raiders' strategy with their picks.\\\",\\\"8bd5ddec-31f0-3437-bcb7-c0aa9441ac10\\\":\\\"Comments include criticism of widespread COVID-19 loan fraud and government oversight failures, with some questioning why more fraud cases and political figures involved haven’t faced consequences. Other comments point to disparities in sentencing and concerns about loan forgiveness despite fraud.\\\",\\\"f4909667-7c7e-3112-b0b2-7b94285c6d21\\\":\\\"Comments include allegations of corruption and misuse of taxpayer money involving Corey Lewandowski and Kristi Noem in a DHS ad campaign, with many suggesting President Trump is upset he didn't receive a cut. The discussion also includes criticism of no-bid contracts and concerns over government waste and favoritism.\\\",\\\"80009e8c-0d3b-4dbb-adde-56e52dab2033\\\":\\\"Comments include views that Ronda Rousey accurately highlights low UFC fighter pay compared to other sports, with some noting UFC's focus on profits over athletes. Other comments criticize Rousey’s past performance and question her current relevance in the sport.\\\",\\\"61de57e0-4077-439a-acaf-257f9771f3cf\\\":\\\"Comments include praise for Bam Adebayo’s 83-point game but also criticism of the NBA’s lack of defense and excessive free throws, with many comparing it unfavorably to past eras and Kobe Bryant’s more efficient 81-point game. Other comments point to the Wizards’ weak defense and rule changes enabling high scoring.\\\",\\\"f42c1e16-088b-33fa-a697-2833c9c63f33\\\":\\\"Comments include calls for the mother and boyfriend to receive life sentences and for the boy and siblings to find loving homes and therapy. Other comments point to the need for stricter child welfare checks and express hope the child heals from the abuse.\\\",\\\"a3132e70-c078-3802-a63d-1dbed8e10b4e\\\":\\\"Comments include criticism of the government’s handling of the treasure hunter’s case, with some claiming unfair imprisonment and disputes over ownership of the gold coins. Other comments point to skepticism about the missing coins and the legal battles involving investors and authorities.\\\",\\\"509e346f-b69c-3438-8f08-4712263292cd\\\":\\\"Comments include views that the couple's financial tension stems from differing spending and saving habits, with the husband controlling finances tightly and the wife feeling \\\\\\\"broke\\\\\\\" due to limited spending money despite a high net worth. Other comments point to communication issues and debate the plausibility of their claimed wealth.\\\",\\\"70968e93-7264-3cfc-8eb7-a62d9db5ab00\\\":\\\"Comments include critiques of the winner's money management despite receiving over $3 million, with many saying he should have saved or invested rather than retire early; other comments point to the risks of relying on company-backed lifetime payments, urging lump sum options and financial planning. The discussion also includes allegations that PCH's business model was unsustainable and warnings about trusting such promises.\\\",\\\"3e95c89a-c0cd-3bab-9d4e-01ab81f1ecf1\\\":\\\"Comments include skepticism about the former superyacht worker’s claims and focus on her appearance and alleged adult entertainment career, while others discuss the behavior of wealthy men on yachts as expected. The discussion also includes comparisons to known scandals and doubts about her motives and experiences.\\\",\\\"f66d5ab6-a4d0-3065-9919-4fcebb6c0b02\\\":\\\"Comments include mixed reactions to Liza Minnelli's claim that Gene Hackman was rude on the set of \\\\\\\"Lucky Lady,\\\\\\\" with some defending Hackman's professionalism and others criticizing Minnelli for speaking ill of the deceased decades later. The discussion also includes reflections on Hollywood dynamics and respect for privacy after death.\\\",\\\"216e96d6-f139-3c75-bc2d-036d0fb2df8d\\\":\\\"Comments include skepticism about the island's safety amid climate change and hurricanes, noting its low elevation and vulnerability. Other comments point to the extreme wealth gap, with elites isolating themselves in luxury while critics question the practicality and security of such exclusive bunkers.\\\",\\\"48fb59b7-f68e-3ba5-9e97-f9b30e188763\\\":\\\"Comments include praise for the wife’s grace in requesting leniency for students involved in a tragic, accidental death during a prank. Other comments point to the lack of malicious intent and suggest that guilt and counseling are sufficient consequences.\\\",\\\"2ac91034-16a1-36c8-8945-d70d0bf714da\\\":\\\"Comments include skepticism about how Sen. Cory Booker's proposed tax break for incomes up to $75,000 would be funded, with concerns over increased deficit and lack of spending cuts. Other comments point to calls for fairer tax contributions, closing loopholes, and balancing budgets rather than vote-driven tax promises.\\\",\\\"4d7f0a2e-4ad9-412c-9155-3a57910be9c0\\\":\\\"Comments include praise for Dakota Johnson's appearance and modeling success, with some noting her acting skills and family background. Other comments point to debates about nepotism, comparisons to Sydney Sweeney, and views on beauty standards in modeling.\\\",\\\"d9d1e26b-a724-3e73-bd4e-7768064ef3b2\\\":\\\"Comments include observations of record warm winters and drought concerns in the western US, while others question data accuracy or attribute changes to natural cycles. Certain comments criticize misinformation campaigns and political stances, mentioning President Trump and former President Biden in climate debates.\\\",\\\"05ff8440-a680-374e-a173-db6159dcff48\\\":\\\"Comments include criticism of the lawsuit against Pima County Sheriff Chris Nanos as frivolous and unrelated to Nancy Guthrie, with many questioning its merit and connection to her case. Other comments express frustration over media clickbait linking the two stories.\\\",\\\"dc777226-3d70-3490-a7f7-89854b3d2214\\\":\\\"Comments include concerns over the poor state of U.S. bridges, with many blaming lack of maintenance and federal funding diverted to wars and tax cuts for the wealthy. Other comments point to former President Biden’s infrastructure bill as a positive step amid criticism of President Trump’s policies.\\\",\\\"c33550cd-e110-3f8c-af2b-f7fa75560bc6\\\":\\\"Comments include skepticism about the former FBI agent's claim that Nancy Guthrie was probably alive when abducted, with many finding it obvious or questioning the logic of kidnapping a deceased person. Other comments point to frustration over the slow investigation and lack of new information in the case.\\\",\\\"e86db914-470b-35fd-b0ca-7541cc6d73d7\\\":\\\"Comments include support for Justice Gorsuch’s view that parole violations should require jury trials as a constitutional right, while others argue parole revocations traditionally do not involve juries and offenders must face consequences. The discussion also includes claims that the Supreme Court’s decisions are politically motivated, especially regarding President Trump’s influence.\\\",\\\"f27efc15-0ee4-4de0-92d4-85424cbc2af9\\\":\\\"Comments include debates on Jim Carrey’s altered appearance sparking theories about cosmetic work and aging pressures in Hollywood, with some noting shifting beauty standards for men. Others emphasize natural aging acceptance and question the focus on looks over talent.\\\",\\\"167e0395-de5e-3b70-955f-4592f7f7399b\\\":\\\"Comments include skepticism about whether President Trump personally pays for the Florsheim shoes given to staffers, with many noting they are mostly made overseas and questioning the use of taxpayer money. Other comments point to the shoes as symbols of control and fear within the administration, reflecting concerns about loyalty and conformity.\\\",\\\"7873bb35-16aa-3e92-ace1-d2f35f5ce1f1\\\":\\\"Comments include views that Rep. Kevin Kiley's shift to independent status is a strategic move to win reelection amid redistricting, not a true break from the Republican Party, as he plans to continue caucusing with them. Other comments point to frustration with partisan politics and call for more independents to reduce gridlock.\\\",\\\"997c7270-620f-3f78-a5aa-bfc0e80e3ce0\\\":\\\"Comments include praise for Kendra Wilkinson embracing natural aging and rejecting societal pressure for youth, with many noting she looks healthy and normal for 40. Other comments point to the cruelty of social media critics and the unrealistic beauty standards celebrities face.\\\",\\\"ece44db0-9d84-4c7b-a33d-15e073c15f73\\\":\\\"Comments include criticism of the Hawks and NBA for proposing a strip club promotion, seen as inappropriate for families and damaging to the league's image. Other comments point to perceived double standards regarding gambling and alcohol promotions and debate cultural acceptance in Atlanta.\\\",\\\"da009da8-1bb0-342a-a1b1-03be75d41181\\\":\\\"Comments include criticism of the article's misleading headline and lack of a clear photo of Princess Lilibet, with many questioning the use of \\\\\\\"grown-up\\\\\\\" for a four-year-old and the focus on Meghan Markle. Other comments point to debates over royal titles and privacy concerns.\\\",\\\"28fba826-b65f-4a0e-a8f6-dbae05648d21\\\":\\\"Comments include mixed views on NFL free agency moves, praising some team upgrades while criticizing others like the Cardinals and Chiefs. Certain comments express skepticism about expert predictions and player signings, with some linking team performance to broader leadership themes under President Trump.\\\",\\\"a4298a84-5baf-3cf7-adfc-dc209f246e89\\\":\\\"Comments include critiques of Timothée Chalamet's dismissive remarks on opera and ballet, highlighting the dedication those arts require and their lasting cultural value. Other comments point to generational shifts in audience interest and suggest Chalamet’s comments reflect youthful immaturity rather than informed opinion.\\\",\\\"d820153c-2077-3eb3-815d-0367e78bdde2\\\":\\\"Comments include concerns about tourists' disrespect and rule-breaking in national parks, with many calling for stricter enforcement, higher fines, and better funding for park staff. Other comments point to entitlement, lack of consequences, and overcrowding as key issues harming these natural spaces.\\\",\\\"e9307668-d300-3296-ac38-eae3a8b993bb\\\":\\\"Comments include calls for deposit and recycling programs to reduce disposable vape litter causing flat tires, with many noting broader issues of careless littering from smokers and construction debris. Other comments point to environmental hazards from lithium batteries and societal disregard for proper trash disposal.\\\",\\\"c8e9710f-7695-37a7-8a3b-dc86ddfdcc32\\\":\\\"Comments include criticism of \\\\\\\"rolling coal\\\\\\\" as illegal, immature, and harmful behavior that endangers others and damages diesel engines. Other comments point to calls for stricter laws, vehicle impoundment, and fines to stop this practice and protect clean air.\\\",\\\"192c87fd-2594-38df-9f64-d57479a8c629\\\":\\\"Comments include many criticizing Gen Z men’s traditional views on marriage as insecure and outdated, with some linking these attitudes to conservative influences like President Trump and MAGA. Others point to economic and cultural factors, emphasizing the need for equal partnerships and respect in relationships.\\\",\\\"c9fabf2c-e083-4504-9a61-81eafbba744c\\\":\\\"Comments include varied views on celebrities naming antidepressants, with some praising destigmatization and others warning it may glamorize medication or promote overprescription; the discussion also covers concerns about side effects, the importance of therapy and lifestyle changes, and skepticism about Big Pharma's influence.\\\",\\\"5cb12974-d3a2-37bf-9cf3-c780ef20b465\\\":\\\"Comments include many expressing skepticism about the happiness and equality in the triad, suggesting the wife may be sacrificing self-respect to keep her husband, who is accused of cheating and using her financially. Other comments point to concerns over dishonesty and unhealthy dynamics rather than true polyamory.\\\",\\\"4ceb2a06-71b0-3863-9b3d-76795fccb1cf\\\":\\\"Comments include concerns about systemic failures allowing mentally ill individuals to access firearms despite prior Baker Act interventions and losing custody of children. Other comments point to frustrations with weak gun laws, inconsistent justice, and the need for better mental health care and legal reforms.\\\",\\\"859fdb98-7cee-38c2-ab10-d1c5ae14ff98\\\":\\\"Comments include widespread allegations of Republican corruption linked to COVID relief fraud and skepticism about justice fairness, with many expecting a pardon from President Trump. Other comments point to political bias, comparing Republican misconduct to Democratic actions and questioning media coverage.\\\",\\\"fbd0631d-b20c-3253-bf26-fe9fac17413e\\\":\\\"Comments include some questioning whether making faces at flight attendants is enough to signal a problem, suggesting direct communication would be more effective. Other comments point to proper procedures for addressing issues during flights.\\\",\\\"b5ad0775-5f22-3009-9078-8a889daa71ba\\\":\\\"Comments include views that Tig Notaro ended her friendship with Cheryl Hines due to unbalanced communication and political differences tied to Hines's husband, RFK Jr. Other comments point to broader concerns about political intolerance harming personal relationships and question Tig's portrayal as a victim.\\\",\\\"58a8c445-44f2-3edd-9786-3582796cd93c\\\":\\\"Comments include expressions of concern about domestic violence as a serious issue and calls for justice, while others link the crime to cultural and regional stereotypes, particularly associating the accused with MAGA and red-state Kentucky. The discussion also includes skepticism about legal outcomes and reflections on victims' struggles.\\\",\\\"f2896ad1-c548-3b49-99fc-d33867333f6d\\\":\\\"Comments include calls for a non-partisan judiciary and concerns about ideological courts, with some seeing the justice's retirement as a chance for liberal progress in Wisconsin. Other comments express worry about losing conservative influence and question the impact on constitutional rights.\\\",\\\"07b9af95-50e5-40d5-b6f9-f7b31b3e8754\\\":\\\"Comments include many Chiefs fans doubting Travis Kelce's performance and urging him to retire, citing decline and distractions from his relationship with Taylor Swift. Other comments point to continued support for his skills and hope he contributes to another strong season.\\\",\\\"a72ba1f4-0e5c-3300-b5f2-d75cd375f05b\\\":\\\"Comments include advice that with $1.5 million in IRAs and $4,500 monthly Social Security, retirees can live comfortably if debt-free and budget wisely, while others stress planning for taxes, healthcare costs, and caution about financial advisor fees. The discussion also includes skepticism about the article’s relevance to average Americans.\\\",\\\"4a955b92-0afe-3d2b-92de-accc8a659fc6\\\":\\\"Comments include criticism of the Catholic Church's handling of financial crimes and calls for stronger accountability, with some noting the bishop’s arrest contrasts with past protection of child abuse cases. Other comments point to broader concerns about institutional corruption and skepticism toward religious leadership.\\\",\\\"6d0da2f5-6fec-4b1a-bf4a-d16de7086462\\\":\\\"Comments include debate over whether a 10-year prison sentence for cheating in a Texas fishing tournament is excessive, with some suggesting fines and bans instead. Other comments point to repeated cheating in fishing contests and compare the punishment to leniency for more serious crimes.\\\",\\\"da273c18-fdbe-36e0-8df0-0b11a8bd04fc\\\":\\\"Comments include criticism of California's criminal justice system for releasing repeat offenders and skepticism about suing the city over the ambulance theft, with many blaming crime policies and calling the lawsuit a money grab. Other comments point to the need for tougher crime laws and question the family's legal strategy.\\\",\\\"41500e6f-57d5-3d51-b135-b760aa6c9ad4\\\":\\\"Comments include debates on who is the NBA GOAT, with many arguing Michael Jordan's dominance and impact, while others highlight Bill Russell's 11 championships or Kareem Abdul-Jabbar's longevity and records; the discussion also notes Isiah Thomas's ongoing rivalry with Jordan affecting his views.\\\",\\\"3e880711-4216-3357-8b9e-ae00698415ed\\\":\\\"Comments include mixed views on cannabis, with some praising its benefits for liver health and criticizing government and pharmaceutical industries for opposing it, while others see it as merely an excuse for drug addiction. The discussion also includes skepticism about government claims on cannabis.\\\",\\\"bc04450d-f826-3e95-91ce-890d09bb4510\\\":\\\"Comments include widespread skepticism about Nancy Guthrie’s survival, with many suggesting she likely died shortly after her disappearance and that the case involves family or professional foul play. Other comments point to frustrations over investigative delays, speculative expert opinions, and theories involving staged evidence or criminal motives.\\\",\\\"dad7be47-ab64-3641-9492-5f695eae40fc\\\":\\\"Comments include many questioning Dwight Howard's sexuality and criticizing his ex-wife's appearance and behavior, with some suggesting the marriage was a facade. Other comments point to issues of trust, money, and the challenges of celebrity relationships, while a few express concern for the children involved.\\\",\\\"98444be4-0afc-3bb1-8116-6347f94a68ef\\\":\\\"Comments include expressions of sadness over the loss of Jordan Jones while breaking up a bar fight and warnings that nothing good happens late at night. Other comments point to cultural issues and debate the wisdom of intervening in violent disputes.\\\",\\\"208fe228-f2b2-4a6c-a058-dcab1f01aca7\\\":\\\"Comments include critiques of the protein obsession as a food fad, noting cheese provides protein and mac and cheese need not include meat; others highlight balanced diets and caution against excess protein. The discussion also includes skepticism about dietary trends and calls for moderation.\\\",\\\"e8888308-f99c-4e40-9217-5f8d833cc2af\\\":\\\"Comments include mixed reactions to the Donna Kelce home renovation memes, with some finding the news wholesome or relatable, while others question its newsworthiness and express frustration over media focus on celebrity families instead of more important topics. The discussion also includes remarks on privacy concerns and comparisons to other public figures.\\\",\\\"b5c09117-9125-3a07-aeb1-f8bc2129d881\\\":\\\"Comments include critiques of the MAGA influencer’s warning about Pixar’s \\\\\\\"Hoppers,\\\\\\\" noting many classic Disney and Pixar films have dark themes and questioning the influencer’s biblical knowledge. Other comments point to perceived hypocrisy in MAGA’s Christian claims and emphasize the movie is fictional entertainment, not a religious text.\\\",\\\"7fa56701-69bd-3faa-a25e-ac8cc9cdc6f0\\\":\\\"Comments include criticism of President Trump’s impact on America’s global reputation, with many saying MAGA supporters face hostility abroad due to his policies and behavior. Other comments point to political identity causing social divides and reluctance among Trump voters to disclose their support internationally.\\\",\\\"ab86d3dc-a6b4-37a4-bf10-7ffefbd9321d\\\":\\\"Comments include calls from moderate Democrats to move past Vice President Kamala Harris for the 2028 nomination, urging the party to start over with a more electable, centrist candidate. Other comments point to frustration with party leadership, lack of fair primaries, and a desire for fresh faces to defeat President Trump.\\\",\\\"b18eed00-446f-3acd-897f-982fc6764bfc\\\":\\\"Comments include many urging Valerie Bertinelli to respect Eddie Van Halen’s widow by not revisiting their past, noting he was married to another woman when he died. Other comments point to her repeated mentions as attempts to stay relevant or promote a book.\\\",\\\"a71a6198-196f-3e24-bbec-7235f6401589\\\":\\\"Comments include mixed reactions to Jordon Hudson's rope dress, with some noting its environmental message and others criticizing its style and appropriateness for a charity event. The discussion also includes remarks about her relationship with Bill Belichick and skepticism about her motives.\\\",\\\"a5b3073e-69b8-345f-85c9-1d62fc198fbb\\\":\\\"Comments include concerns about the dangers of social media for children, with many questioning why a 12-year-old had access to platforms like Snapchat and was awake at 1 a.m. Other comments point to parental responsibility and the need for more urgent attention to the case.\\\",\\\"08c5a909-1587-3976-8507-d55b59f8e5cb\\\":\\\"Comments include many sharing personal experiences with Bell's palsy, emphasizing uncertainty about surgery and urging caution as recovery can take time; other comments point to possible causes like stress or infection, while some express hope for Bristol Palin's improvement and question the timing of cosmetic procedures.\\\",\\\"bbde9695-c2b8-3250-a9da-6bc310bda636\\\":\\\"Comments include sadness over the teacher’s lonely death and questions about why no one noticed her absence sooner; other comments point to concerns about school custodial duties and the unclear circumstances of her passing before classes started. Certain comments express respect for her dedication despite her age.\\\",\\\"e934d1a3-5a5b-3ed9-bc25-332f5c0bcb3d\\\":\\\"Comments include many accusing Dak Prescott’s ex-fiancée of seeking money and rejecting a prenup despite having children with him, while others highlight expected infidelity among high-profile athletes. The discussion also includes views on athlete relationships and financial arrangements.\\\",\\\"5de143d0-6ffb-4f68-93d2-8e8051f185a1\\\":\\\"Comments include criticism of the Jets for trading for Geno Smith despite his poor performance, with many calling it a move to tank for a top draft pick. Other comments point to the Raiders benefiting slightly by offloading Smith's contract, while some see the trade as typical Jets mismanagement.\\\",\\\"f84b1332-f520-3ad4-99e8-f03820ebd964\\\":\\\"Comments include many sharing personal struggles with State Farm canceling policies after drone roof inspections and questioning the fairness of insurance practices. Other comments point to privacy concerns, legal challenges, and calls to drop or sue insurers over these tactics.\\\",\\\"1f4de431-2002-3324-ba26-0d0898dcc79f\\\":\\\"Comments include skepticism about Darron Lee’s claim that a victim’s severe injuries resulted from a shower fall, with many mocking the implausibility and criticizing his use of ChatGPT for advice. Other comments point to Lee’s wasted potential and discuss accountability, while some mention concerns about AI’s role in legal matters.\\\",\\\"0269d2b4-f1e2-452d-93a1-2425cb55d440\\\":\\\"Comments include skepticism about Kyler Murray returning to baseball due to his long absence, age, and lack of minor league experience, with many doubting his work ethic and ability to succeed in either sport. Other comments point to financial and career longevity factors influencing his choices.\\\"}},\\\"integratedFeedVariant\\\":null,\\\"goodNewsArticles\\\":{\\\"goodNewsArticles\\\":[\\\"0239b3d3-4fa0-3ce1-af96-a3731fe4c60a\\\",\\\"0c8bc930-6ff4-3afd-88f0-50635dd42a17\\\",\\\"0e3e1e6e-d6f7-372c-a1fc-ae816dc53c8d\\\",\\\"10f909cc-6d72-333e-a53e-94763d57f00e\\\",\\\"12647154-39f8-3922-a8db-4101ffbbb65c\\\",\\\"14723013-4bb8-37de-95d6-f6f0fb7e403e\\\",\\\"155204e4-8923-34f7-8b1b-cdf1b2711039\\\",\\\"1ae85411-5b47-331e-91ed-347f95c27d29\\\",\\\"20b59fac-e7b3-3a47-857c-c5448e0aaba0\\\",\\\"2d987fa4-a594-3aed-a150-e25d9365c3f0\\\",\\\"309f1a72-ef39-396f-a1d2-f30899b72d46\\\",\\\"329339b2-9c16-3033-b354-a552c04fe982\\\",\\\"37111e0c-c141-3c7f-9c90-c1f4a35c4916\\\",\\\"390a0508-e551-35d0-8db0-8980e1a5ce7a\\\",\\\"46d406d3-e039-36b9-880b-1f185a7bba34\\\",\\\"4a5c45ec-25bf-3fc7-b351-d33c5c6d82b1\\\",\\\"4b0af473-781c-31d3-9948-75d428